fi.jumi.actors.listeners

Interface MessageListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NullMessageListener, PrintStreamMessageLogger

    public interface MessageListener
    Gets notified about all messages that actors send and receive. Can also listen for all commands submitted to an Executor by wrapping it in getListenedExecutor(java.util.concurrent.Executor).
    See Also:
    NullMessageListener, PrintStreamMessageLogger
